title: Glee: The Ultimate Fifth Season, Part Two
description:
The second part of Glee's fifth season, with the remaining 7 episodes.

14. New New York
15. Bash
16. Tested
17. Opening Night
18. The Back-Up Plan
19. Old Dog, New Tricks
20. The Untitled Rachel Berry Project

This package also includes the music released through these 7 episodes.

As an added bonus, in separate episode folders, I have included the original versions of the songs featured on Glee. This is something I do myself.
